by aitboudad at 2015-04-26T16:06:46Z

@nicolasdewez no it's ok I'll merge into `2.8` but for the next time try to choose the right Branch :)

* `2.3`  fixing a bug.
* `2.8`  adding a new feature which is backward compatible;
* `master`, adding a new and backward incompatible feature.

see http://symfony.com/doc/2.7/contributing/code/patches.html#choose-the-right-branch
